aosctl index — production index control (/opt/aos + system scope)

Usage:
  aosctl index status|start|stop|restart|logs|health|doctor
  aosctl index enable|disable
  aosctl index deploy [--dry-run] [--src=PATH] [--dst=PATH]
__INDEX_HELP__
      ;;
